    "description": "CRAZY GUY is the story of a space tramp who travels across worlds with the simple goal of clearing out enemies. You joined a war nomad as he explored a small cluster of enemies on a secret planet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTogether with the nomads, you quickly determined that the planet had been invaded by space terrorists. In each sector, a certain group of enemies with the latest weapons settled down and who knows what plans they have in mind. You have nothing left but to go into a dishonest battle and clean up all the enemies and eliminate their weapons.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features:<br />\r\n• Classic 2D platformer<br />\r\n• Various weapons and enemies<br />\r\n• Nice pixel graphics",
